Release 0.01 must-have's:
-------------------------

 - Site admin (OK)
 - Channel register (OK)
 - Channel admin (OK)
 - New/edit story (OK)
 - Clean theme and clean widgets
 - utf8 input/upload (OK)
 - utf8 filename, category, title, abstract etc. (OK)
 - Storylist (OK)
 - Picture with next/prev (OK)
 - Error check
 - Install doc
 - License tags


